i love working with customers sales has really influenced everything i do it has instilled in me the important traits of operating with a sense of urgency and listening to people jeffrey r immelt love listening sales many bought into the idea that america could go from a technologybased exportoriented powerhouse to a servicesled consumptionbased economy  and somehow still expect to prosper that idea was flat wrong our economy tilted instead toward the quicker profits of financial services jeffrey r immelt financial america economy is france a completely open market to ge no of course not i think were more discerning about china because its china and theyre big and theyre more concerning but the best global companies are ones that are nuanced jeffrey r immelt best think more i grew up in cincinnati ohio and my parents are really right wingers my dad watches like five or six hours of fox news every day and stuff like that jeffrey r immelt dad parents day i think we should have basically the same tax policy that germany japan the uk everybody else has which is a tax rate in the mids and no loopholes zero the us has the most antiquated tax system and that means some people are going to pay more taxes and some people are going to pay less jeffrey r immelt people think some people i do business in  countries none of them is perfect there is not even one country that i think of and i am like god that did everything that i wanted it to do jeffrey r immelt business god i am when i was a young guy when i first started with ge jack welch sent us all to japan because in those days japan was gonna crush us and we learned a lot about japan when we were there but over the subsequent  years the japanese companies all fell behind and the reason why they fell behind is because they didnt globalize jeffrey r immelt young why over every leader needs to clearly explain the top three things the organization is working on if you cant then youre not leading well jeffrey r immelt leader organization you there is no real magic to being a good leader but at the end of every week you have to spend your time around the things that are really important setting priorities measuring outcomes and rewarding them jeffrey r immelt time good week when you take over a company like ge you think youre going to visit  businesses youre going to go see the factories you havent seen before youre going to see a site in texas and one in canada and stuff like that that has fallen by the wayside jeffrey r immelt think you canada president obama has asked me to chair his new presidents council on jobs and competitiveness jeffrey r immelt me new chair business leaders should provide expertise in service of our country my predecessors at ge have done so as have leaders of many other great american companies jeffrey r immelt business great service as one of americas largest exporters ge remains committed to producing more products in the united states which is our home and largest market jeffrey r immelt home america more ge sells more than  percent of its products to the private sector where americas future must be built but government can help business invest in our shared future jeffrey r immelt business future government you can stay too long in a job thats for sure but by the same token in the  years i have been ceo of ge there have been four ceos of toshiba so theres too short a time to do it and theres too long a time to do it jeffrey r immelt time job short im a complete globalist i think like a global ceo but im an american i run an american company but in order for ge to be successful in the coming years ive gotta sell my products in every corner of the world jeffrey r immelt world american successful i think this notion that its the population of the us against the big companies is just wrong jeffrey r immelt population think wrong share this page cite this page citation find on amazon jeffrey r immelt related authors steve jobs warren buffett henry ford bill gates j